ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce District Saint-Rémi CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DISTRICT SAINT-RÉMI, in Quebec (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE HEMMINGFORD-NAPIERVILLE-SAINT-RÉMI; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to Napierville, Saint-Cyprien de Napierville, Sherrington, Saint-Bernard de Lacolle, Saint-Jacques-le-Mineur, Hemmingford Village and Hemmingford Township.
